Memory Regions

```c
// include/exec/memory.h

// Base memory region
struct MemoryRegion {
    const MemoryRegionOps *ops;
    void *opaque;
    MemoryRegion *container;
    Int128 size;           // Size in bytes
    hwaddr addr;           // Base address
