· PIC (Programmable Interrupt Controller): Legacy x86 (8259)
· APIC (Advanced Programmable Interrupt Controller): x86 SMP
· GIC (Generic Interrupt Controller): ARM
· PLIC (Platform-Level Interrupt Controller): RISC-V

